    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>JAMs</strong></u> is a clicker game with Steam items themed around art and music, served in jars.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Initially, the scope of the game will be a quite simple clicker game with items but will evolve over time to become something special.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is <i>free to play</i> so everyone will be able to get drops, but with the <strong><u>Extra Drops DLC</u></strong> you will get a few more, it will be a fair distribution and there may be a few special items only available through the item shop in the future, but for now the daily drop creations are all that we have ever had.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The schedule of items being removed from the drop pool will be a reliable thing and rotate quite frequently, so you will need to idle the game all the time in order to get all the drops.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is art-and-music themed, so if you are an artist (or just love it!) be sure to join the <strong>JAMs Discord Server</strong> and follow along with the project as we grow!</p>",
